{"tid":941254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB明年平均加薪3%及一個月花紅","createTime":"2018-12-14T15:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T00:53:24.000Z","uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2c50fb08864ddcce8454592a164d07d79b0a3e88","tid":941254,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"無綫藝員黃心穎、楊明、莊思明、伍允龍、劉穎鏇、張名雅等晚上在將軍澳電視城出席《TVB職藝員聯歡晚宴2018》，晚上招待超過二千位員工享用盆菜宴，集團行政總裁李寶安席間公布加薪幅度，平均加薪3%，及平均一個月花紅，職藝員接獲喜訊齊齊歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n對於公司宣布加人工，心穎稱藝員與職員合約不同，沒有份加人工，但戥同事開心。可會要求加騷錢？她說：「又冇，情願要多啲機會，好過金錢。」"},{"pid":"ab21e87f76512961e96379152abcf562a2f06276","tid":941254,"uid":151496,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"做藝員好似好低 低薪，加3%，好少"},{"pid":"051b288a3e72bf7057b1c02ac76813c7c3286da8","tid":941254,"uid":136611,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"仲有多餘錢加薪? tvb 隻股票日日咁跌法"},{"pid":"0019ed60c7dd8f1b41daa2ed5ebc7a6156385f8d","tid":941254,"uid":114692,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e335ea435af75b31a6164f245444b75cbf817db","tid":941254,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"051b288a3e72bf7057b1c02ac76813c7c3286da8","tid":941254,"uid":136611,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"仲有多餘錢加薪? tvb 隻股票日日咁跌法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"3%一年都係幾千萬"},{"pid":"ee172c64afb2a6bf82e723c3a0d92cd4834c2100","tid":941254,"uid":2471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab21e87f76512961e96379152abcf562a2f06276","tid":941254,"uid":151496,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"做藝員好似好低 低薪，加3%，好少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"1xk"},{"pid":"2fe4bb6b1a74e2591bd7b72a72bba24616cd961a","tid":941254,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14